{
  "texts": [
    "Bars show the average improvement of PRAUC scores across the 50 evaluations with respect to the noskill classifier; error bars denote one standard deviation of the PRAUC.",
    "Full precision-recall curves for each case can be found in Supplementary Fig. 2.",
    "C Performance of FlowGAT in cross-testing across different carbon sources; in each case, the model was trained on one graph and tested on the nodes of all other graphs, totalling 90 cross-test evaluations.",
    "The color bar indicates the improvement in PRAUC over the no-skill classifier; the bubble radius denotes the graphto-graph distance computed as the Jansen-Shannon divergence between the distribution of node features.",
    "In panels (B, C), the performance improvement was computed as 100 × PRAUC FlowGAT À PRAUC no-skill À Á =PRAUC no-skill."
  ]
}